    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302550/extras/2f62af4dd4c3b562fea15856f3a9d92a.avif?t=1770945988\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302550/extras_big/2f62af4dd4c3b562fea15856f3a9d92a.webp?t=1770945988 width=1560 height=1103 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两眼一睁，便看见扫地机器人眼巴巴地看着你，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它说你是舰长，肩负着带领船员探索人类宜居地的重任，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >硬着头皮召回因爆炸失散的船员们，不曾想一个比一个重量级——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是，鸡飞狗跳的舰上生活便开始了——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >频发的神秘事件、潜在的杀人犯、各怀鬼胎的成员——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302550/extras/9291d542df3dd77e539083dd80d749aa.avif?t=1770945988\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302550/extras_big/9291d542df3dd77e539083dd80d749aa.webp?t=1770945988 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及这艘舰启航的真正目的……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >周旋于真相与隐秘之间，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而不讲理的羁绊却在怀疑与探求中悄然建立……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△简介</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本游戏中，您将扮演一位失忆的舰长，需要召回因为船体爆炸而失散的船员。毫无疑问，这些人的到来将会引发新的事件。您会在扫地机器人“萝卜”的陪伴下，靠您的“洞察力”和与他们互动来找出事件的真相——而一切线索最后都将会指向导致船体爆炸的真凶。与此同时，您可以自由与您的船员们发展情感关系（友谊/爱情），了解他们有助于您找到最后的真凶；他们也将作为您观察的透镜，映射出这个您“完全不记得”的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△游戏玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏结合了AVG和RPG的玩法，您可以阅读视觉小说，也可以操纵玩家角色调查场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏计划设置有别于往常AVG的情感发展模式，将在之后的更新的demo中呈现（第一个demo并未收录）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△更新计划</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏在正式版上架前，预计会上传三版demo（删档），每个demo都会有新的内容/功能，也欢迎您随时留下不同demo版本的游玩反馈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△DEMO内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情：呈现了第一个章节的内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >登场的男主：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302550/extras/e567f09493f98c6101dece0f7d1fd7ab.avif?t=1770945988\" width=918 height=918 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正义凛然好青年？——张林思</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“<i>在舰上的这段时间请随意差遣我！我会努力成为舰长的得力助手的！</i>”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是——他好像是杀人犯？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
